How to use:

1. Put the lexer_vala.* files in your (...)/lexers directory (e.g. /usr/share/codeblocks/lexers on Debian Linux).
2. Restart Code::Blocks.
3. Write a custom makefile for building your project and set C::B to use it (Project menu -> Properties -> This is a custom Makefile).
4. ???
5. PROFIT!!!!1

Brought to you by http://github.com/inequation.

Enjoy!
